firebase-crashlytics.author: Matthew Robertson
firebase-crashlytics.message:
Don't use recursion in TrimmedThrowableData to avoid stack overflow (#5310)

Don't use recursion in TrimmedThrowableData. This fixes an issue when
exceptions with long caused by chains cause a stack overflow.

Pair with PolinaGo
